                                            </h4>
                                        </div>
                                        <div id="coupon" class="collapse in">
                                            <div class="panel-body">
                                                <div class="col-sm-2">
                                                    <p>Enter your coupon here</p>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="input-group">
                                                    <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Enter your coupon here" />
